## Organization Standards (DevRails)

This project follows DevRails development standards (requires [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)).

### Commands
| Command | What It Does |
|---------|--------------|
| `/fix <description>` | Start bugfix workflow |
| `/feature <description>` | Start feature workflow |
| `/pr` | Create pull request |
| `/commit` | Format commit message |
| `/review` | Code review checklist |
| `/status` | Show state, suggest next |

